s\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the flag\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 4170, \"to\": 4172}, {\"ngram\": \"the normal 12-minute rule\", \"from\": 4196, \"to\": 4221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A wobbly rendition of \\\"The Star-Spangled Banner\\\" was followed by the much-hyped sight of a 62-year-oldTom Cruise(looking increasingly like hisMadame Tussaudsdoppelganger) floating down from the stadium's rafters.\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A wobbly rendition\", \"from\": 4224, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"The Star-Spangled Banner\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4271}, {\"ngram\": \"the much-hyped sight\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4309}, {\"ngram\": \"a 62-year-oldTom\", \"from\": 4313, \"to\": 4329}, {\"ngram\": \"hisMadame Tussaudsdoppelganger\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4393}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium's rafters\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LA native acts Red Hot Chili Peppers,Billie EilishandSnoop Dogg, played us out, live from a sun-soaked Venice Beach.\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4452, \"end\": 4473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Red Hot Chili Peppers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}, {\"begin\": 4540, \"end\": 4552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice,_Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999752490115, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Venice Beach\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice,_Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Venice,_Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Billie EilishandSnoop Dogg\", \"from\": 4474, \"to\": 4500}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A stark warning, if it were needed, of what the US is willing to invest in maintaining its soft power hegemony.\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4602, \"end\": 4604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"score\": 0.9986749168690362, \"rank\": 0.0011064969681401726, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Billboard_Hot_100\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A stark warning\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4569}, {\"ngram\": \"its soft power hegemony\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This closing ceremony has thrown into stark relief the issues with the games' curtain-raiser.\", \"from\": 4667, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This closing ceremony\", \"from\": 4667, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"stark relief\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4717}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4728}, {\"ngram\": \"the games' curtain-raiser\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Stade de France - an 80,000-seater stadium - proved a sufficiently large canvas for the theatrical elements of proceedings.\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Stade de France\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4780}, {\"ngram\": \"a sufficiently large canvas\", \"from\": 4817, \"to\": 4844}, {\"ngram\": \"the theatrical elements\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4872}, {\"ngram\": \"proceedings\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And unlike the rain-smudged camera shots across the Seine, the joy and excitement was plain to see on individual athlete's faces.\", \"from\": 4889, \"to\": 5018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4941, \"end\": 4946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.38780080537